Ridge — A Civic Ecology of Breathable Continuity
Ridge is a small, humble, falsifiable civic district designed to model:

unfinished systems

symbolic weather

civic rituals

continuity without closure

epistemic breathability

This repository contains the public Ridge, including:

the Field Guide

the Civic Triad

maintenance logs

Hollowing notes

porch notices

